SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_000_C.speaker: Mole_Wife
SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_000_C.text:
There you are, you useless mole!
You come home so late, I have to
walk around outside to kill time!
Did something happen to you?

SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_000_C.speaker: Mole
SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_000_C.text:
Nothing you need to
worry about, my love.

SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_000_C.speaker: Mole_Wife
SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_000_C.text:
Okay, well... Good.
But did you find any worms?

SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_000_C.speaker: Mole_Wife
SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_000_C.text:
Well, it's better than nothing.
You can leave them here with me.

SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_000_C.speaker: Mole
SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_000_C.text:
Of course, my snugglepuss.
Well, back off to work I go.

SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_000_C.speaker: Mole_Son
SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_000_C.text:
Yaaay! Thank you, Daddy!
Oh, and I found this.
You can have it!

SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_010_C.speaker: Mole
SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_010_C.text:
I secured a nice handful,
my sweet furry lumpykins.

SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_010_C.speaker: Mole_Wife
SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_010_C.text:
Lord, but it's SO boring here
without you. Hurry up and catch
more worms, okay?

SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_010_C.speaker: Mole
SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_010_C.text:
I'm doing what I can, Coste.
...And you take care, Gourmand!

SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_010_C.speaker: Mole_Son
SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_010_C.text:
Yaaay! Thank you, Daddy!
Oh, and I found this.
You can have it!

SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_020_C.speaker: Mole
SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_020_C.text:
I have some worms, my sweet potato.
There aren't a lot, but...

SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_020_C.speaker: Mole_Wife
SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_020_C.text:
Wow. This is just...wow.
Ugh. Fine. Hand 'em over.

SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_020_C.speaker: Mole_Wife
SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_020_C.text:
Well, it should be enough to tide Gourmand
over. Just...come back soon. All right?

SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_020_C.speaker: Mole_Wife
SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_020_C.text:
Don't stick your nose into anything too
dangerous, you fool mole. Gourmand
would be absolutely torn up without you.

SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_020_C.speaker: Mole_Son
SUB_W08_EVAR_COMM_REWARD_EARTHWORM_020_C.text:
Yaaay! Thank you, Daddy!
Oh, and I found this.
You can have it!
